---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout pageKey="best-solar-panels-india.html" headerVariant="policy">

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white py-24">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

<div class="uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-300 text-sm mb-4">
SOLAR EDUCATION CENTER
</div>

<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
Best Solar Panels in India (2026)
</h1>

<p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
Compare leading solar panel brands available in India and learn what matters before making a purchase decision.
</p>

</div>

</section>

<section class="py-20">

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10">
Top Solar Panel Brands
</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">

<table class="w-full">

<thead class="bg-slate-50">

<tr>

<th class="text-left p-4">Brand</th>
<th class="text-left p-4">Manufacturing</th>
<th class="text-left p-4">Suitable For</th>
<th class="text-left p-4">Typical Warranty</th>

</tr>

</thead>

<tbody>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Waaree Energies</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential & Commercial</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Tata Power Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential Projects</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Adani Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential & Industrial</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Vikram Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Premium Installations</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">RenewSys</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential Projects</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Rayzon Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential & Utility Scale</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Premier Energies</td>
<td class="p-4">India</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential & Commercial</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">LONGi Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">Global</td>
<td class="p-4">High Efficiency Residential Systems</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Jinko Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">Global</td>
<td class="p-4">Residential & Commercial</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

<tr class="border-t">
<td class="p-4 font-semibold">Canadian Solar</td>
<td class="p-4">Global</td>
<td class="p-4">Premium Residential & Industrial</td>
<td class="p-4">25-30 Years Performance</td>
</tr>

</tbody>

</table>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="py-20 bg-white">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10">
What Makes A Good Solar Panel?
</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

<div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Efficiency
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Higher efficiency panels generate more electricity from the same roof space.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Warranty
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Look for strong product and performance warranties from reputable manufacturers.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
Manufacturer Reputation
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Established brands generally offer better long-term support and reliability.
</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl">
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">
After-Sales Support
</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600">
Good support can make a significant difference throughout the system lifetime.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="py-20">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10">
Monocrystalline vs Polycrystalline
</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">

<h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">
Monocrystalline
</h3>

<ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">

<li>✓ Higher efficiency</li>
<li>✓ Better aesthetics</li>
<li>✓ Better performance in limited roof space</li>
<li>✓ Most popular choice today</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">

<h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">
Polycrystalline
</h3>

<ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">

<li>✓ Lower cost</li>
<li>✓ Suitable for larger roofs</li>
<li>✓ Proven technology</li>
<li>✓ Less common in new installations</li>

</ul>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="py-20 bg-indigo-50">

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
Need Help Choosing Panels?
</h2>

<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
Our AI assessment considers roof space, electricity usage, budget and system size recommendations.
</p>

<a href="index.html"
class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold">
Calculate My Solar Savings
</a>

</div>

</section>

</BaseLayout>
